Shaw Communications Inc Company Profile

Shaw Communications connects subscribers in the far reaches of Western Canada with cable, internet, and wireless communications services. The company has more than 5 million total customers for its consumer and business services in Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, northwestern Ontario, and Saskatchewan. It has an extensive wired network that includes fiber and coaxial cable, a wireless network, and satellite-based services. It offers a variety of internet services, video entertainment options, and wireless communications plans. Business-oriented services include colocation, cloud computing, and security and compliance offerings. The Shaw family controls the company.
